A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Maddison Hendershot of the Georgia Transportation Alliance
2 for her years of service and commitment to advancing transportation policy in Georgia; and
3 for other purposes.
4 WHEREAS, the Georgia Transportation Alliance is the state's only organization focused
5 solely on identifying and promoting long-term transportation solutions specifically connected
6 to economic development and job creation. GTA is the transportation arm and affiliate of the
7 Georgia Chamber and works closely with the Georgia Department of Transportation, Georgia
8 Ports Authority, and other key stakeholders in Georgia with the goal of ensuring an efficient
9 and safe statewide multi-modal transportation system; and
10 WHEREAS, Maddison Hendershot served as Deputy Director of the Georgia Transportation
11 Alliance from January 2017 to February 2025, during which time she supported the
12 operations of the organization, facilitated board member engagement, and directly
13 coordinated with Georgia General Assembly members and other community leaders; and
14 WHEREAS, Maddison Hendershot has been invaluable in assisting the members of the
15 House of Representatives Committee on Transportation in carrying out their important work,
16 which would not have been as easily done without her help; and
