17 WHEREAS, Maddison Hendershot has organized countless events, making the work of the
18 House of Representatives so much more enjoyable; and
19 WHEREAS, Maddison Hendershot is an outstanding, loving mother of two precious girls,
20 and her husband is a lucky fella; and
21 WHEREAS, Maddison Hendershot is a loved member of the transportation community, and
22 Chairman Rick Jasperse and the 42 members of the House Committee on Transportation
23 wish her well in her new adventure and will miss her greatly.
24 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
25 the members of this body recognize and commend Maddison Hendershot for her efficient,
26 effective, unselfish, and dedicated service and extend the most sincere best wishes for
27 continued success.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
30 Maddison Hendershot.
